Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無遠大理想者 無權享受自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們即將面對諸多的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰勝它們的唯一利器是正義與勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球聯邦軍光輝的歷史中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)}寫上屬於自己的篇章…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弗洛易·奧爾菲亞 代表地球聯邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們這些年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入我們的隊伍並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你們的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.79,0:00:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 宣佈調動情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能做到你那樣 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長期的潛入行動 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了你收集的聯邦軍兵力部署
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰局會對我們維甘有利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 高達的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能報答您的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命你為地球佔領軍司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為伊澤爾坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為維甘的所有人民
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨在所不辭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要讓我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然成了你的長官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信伊澤爾坎特大人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願維甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日重返家園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「維甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是移民計劃失敗的受害者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在火星圈的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新興國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在嚴酷環境下生活的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回那座名為「地球」的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策劃起了規模宏大的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過感覺好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些日子還在上學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同年級的同學大多升學了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊裏也有同樣的課程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 父親說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在需要我作為高達機師去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 又要被周圍人說是特殊待遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到羅瑪麗也參軍了 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外公別提多高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得打電話回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你一定會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為獨當一面的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為明日野家族的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是亞瑟姆·明日野？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣 是倍受期待的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼認識我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽傳聞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令官的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受特別待遇駕駛高達的少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爸也是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和明日野司令官是老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 你老爸和我老爸是鐵哥們兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們也得好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和這艘船真有緣分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的情況是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎啟動 5分鐘後各部門準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾絲艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦接到機密物資運送任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經由 BIG RING
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往 奧利巴諾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加緊準備出航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球嗎 第一次去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？ 我去過喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗 你為什麼參軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 完全沒那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小很聽爸爸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 突然找到了想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非要是聯邦軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實另有緣由吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手 別動嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地司令官專用飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令官按預定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先於本艦前往BIG RING
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大排場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BIG RING司令官有戰艦護航
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天起正式就任達烏內斯司令官的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼年輕的司令官？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為那種傢伙賣命？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然宣佈這麼年輕的人是司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會這樣也無可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難免有人嫉妒你的年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 元氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元氣 元氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是高達？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 可以根據情況需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從飛行狀態變形成人形狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是AGE系統設計出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達二代機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達AGE2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達… AGE2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯老爺子根據你以往的戰鬥數據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新製造出的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙上面裝備的高能多茲步槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有原來兩倍的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等AGE系統的微調工作完成後
