Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 都到齊了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是 天神號機動戰士隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說軍隊上層對他避之不及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次亂駕駛高達的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 性格像極了你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年和你爸一起打仗很帶勁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長認識我父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起我就是你們的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上我的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在沃爾夫隊長手下干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少條命也不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 以前外號好像叫白狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是軍隊裏的王牌機師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不知道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在沃爾夫隊長手下幹過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他雖不是軍人的楷模
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是最棒的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親以前就是那個樣子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無懈可擊 考慮周道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時確實是個有意思的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親是 有意思的小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸是誰不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和其他人同樣是個兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油別讓高達給人搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出航準備完成 全員就位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取道 BIG RING
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載有高達的聯邦戰艦開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是天神號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試探下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令摩挲·蘭古力部隊強行偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載有高達的艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 你也在上面嗎
