Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士機影 6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對照維甘機體數據
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員戰鬥配置…
