Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 戰場
