Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快 大家已經進入戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照例還要對機動戰士形態進行掃瞄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那時間了 馬上出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已
