Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這形態有平時3倍的推進力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
