Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
