Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這樣沒法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
