Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是沃爾夫隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 亞瑟姆
