Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特 麥克斯和阿莉莎拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩台Dorado 接近天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始迎擊
